cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single image dehazing using deep networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel end-to-end learning framework, which involves training a deep neural network to jointly estimate the transmission map and perform dehazing. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on synthetic and real datasets, indicating that it may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM).
